      "writtenOn": "2019-06-18T04:02:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You\u0027re right, but I\u0027d like to set the state early so that secondary startSession calls fail (we can\u0027t catch racy cases of course, it\u0027s best effort). Added a comment to clarify the intention.",
