      "writtenOn": "2019-06-11T15:45:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The logic (specifically error handling logic) looks too complicated.\nHow about introducing a dedicated goroutine to handle session operations, and exchange messages between it and the main thread, and getting rid of doAsync() instead?",
